hwIplpmMib.name: hwIplpmMib
hwIplpmMib.contactinfo: Huawei Industrial Base Bantian, Longgang Shenzhen 518129 People's Republic of China Website: http://www.huawei.com Email: support@huawei.com
hwIplpmMib.description: This MIB describes objects to manage IPLPM (IP Local Performance Monitoring).

hwIplpmLossMeasureEnable.name: hwIplpmLossMeasureEnable
hwIplpmLossMeasureEnable.description: This object indicates that the global loss measure function is 'enabled(1)' or 'disabled(2)'.

hwIplpmLossMeasureColorFlag.name: hwIplpmLossMeasureColorFlag
hwIplpmLossMeasureColorFlag.description: This value indicates the bits of an IP packet used for color measurement. The character '1' represents the bit0 of the FLAGS byte. The character '2' represents the bit6 of the TOS byte. The character '3' represents the bit7 of the TOS byte.

hwIplpmLossMeasureInterval.name: hwIplpmLossMeasureInterval
hwIplpmLossMeasureInterval.description: This object indicates that interval of global loss measure is 'interval1s(1)' or 'interval10s(10)' or 'interval60s(60)' or 'interval600s(600)'.

hwIplpmLossMeasureAlarmEnable.name: hwIplpmLossMeasureAlarmEnable
hwIplpmLossMeasureAlarmEnable.description: This object indicates that the global loss measure alarm function is 'enabled(1)' or 'disabled(2)'.

hwIplpmIntfIfIndex.name: hwIplpmIntfIfIndex
hwIplpmIntfIfIndex.description: The port index of the link loss measure.

hwIplpmIntfInterval.name: hwIplpmIntfInterval
hwIplpmIntfInterval.description: This object indicates that interval of link loss measure is 'interval1s(1)' or 'interval10s(10)' or 'interval60s(60)' or 'interval600s(600)'.

hwIplpmIntfAuthKeyId.name: hwIplpmIntfAuthKeyId
hwIplpmIntfAuthKeyId.description: Authentication identification of the link loss measure.

hwIplpmIntfAuthType.name: hwIplpmIntfAuthType
hwIplpmIntfAuthType.description: Authentication type of the link loss measure. The enumeration 'hmac-sha256(1)' represents the password is sent after being encrypted through hmac-sha256. By default, authentication is not configured.

hwIplpmIntfAuthKey.name: hwIplpmIntfAuthKey
hwIplpmIntfAuthKey.description: The password used as authentication key for link loss measure.

hwIplpmIntfLossMeasureEnable.name: hwIplpmIntfLossMeasureEnable
hwIplpmIntfLossMeasureEnable.description: This object indicates that the link loss measure function is 'enabled(1)' or 'disabled(2)'.

hwIplpmIntfLossMeasureAlarmEnable.name: hwIplpmIntfLossMeasureAlarmEnable
hwIplpmIntfLossMeasureAlarmEnable.description: This object indicates that the link loss measure alarm function is 'enabled(1)' or 'disabled(2)'.

hwIplpmGlobalLossRatioExceed.description: A hwIplpmGlobalLossRatioExceed trap is sent when the global loss ratio exceeds the uppper threshold in continuous five test intervals.

hwIplpmGlobalLossRatioRecovery.description: A hwIplpmGlobalLossRatioRecovery trap is sent when the global loss ratio is under the lower threshold in continuous five test intervals.
